                    <span id="c-1188675601" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1188675601" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1188675601">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/dreamlysh/">鳴鏑校尉文學史</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-05-10</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">有融會貫通之功力，才能做考鏡源流之功夫。雖有以點概面之失，總體瑕不掩瑜~</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1147546446">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1147546446" class="vote-count">2</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1147546446" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1147546446">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/108688063/">文禾斗</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-02-13</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">经学抉原语言没经学导言的语言生动…后者经常会让我想起顾颉刚的秦汉的儒生与方士…蒙先生对廖平的学说十分赞赏，既有继承又有自己的发挥。里面很多的论据别的讲经学的人都不提，或者不解读。谁能知道庄子的一句话就点名了当时的所有学术源流了呢？</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1085829894">
